          <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>The escape:</strong> Match platform to revenue stage. Start with Wix/Squarespace showcase ($17-59/month). Add e-commerce when hitting $2K+ monthly. Migrate to Shopify at $7K+ monthly - e-commerce features pay for themselves in increased conversions. Don't overpay early. Don't under-deliver when you're growing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

